                <div class="modern-grid">
                    <div class="column-3 l-column-2 m-column-0"></div>
                    <div class="column-6 l-column-8 m-column-6 newsroom-internal-body">
                                <div class="spacer-36 m-spacer-24"></div>


                        <h3 class="type-24-light">
                            Design requirements

                        </h3>

                            <div class="spacer-24 m-spacer-16"></div>
                    </div>
                </div>


                    <div class="modern-grid">
                        <div class="column-3 l-column-2 m-column-0"></div>
                        <div class="column-6 l-column-8 m-column-6 newsroom-internal-body">
                            <div class="type-18-light m-type-15">
                                <p>New ADUs in Saratoga must match the primary residence in color, materials, and architectural style. This includes consistent finishes, roof form, and exterior details.</p>

                            </div>
                            <div class="spacer-24 m-spacer-16"></div>
                        </div>
                    </div>




                    <div class="modern-grid">
                        <div class="column-3 l-column-2 m-column-0"></div>
                        <div class="column-6 l-column-8 m-column-6 newsroom-internal-body">
                            <div class="type-18-light m-type-15">
                                <p>If your ADU is taller than 18 feet, adds a second story, or causes the total floor area on the lot to exceed 6,000 square feet, a <a href="https://www.saratoga.ca.us/DocumentCenter/View/2906/Technical-Review-Submittal-Checklist" target="_blank">design review application</a> will be required before permits can be issued.</p>

                            </div>
                            <div class="spacer-24 m-spacer-16"></div>
                        </div>
                    </div>




                <div class="modern-grid">
                    <div class="column-3 l-column-2 m-column-0"></div>
                    <div class="column-6 l-column-8 m-column-6 newsroom-internal-body">
                                <div class="spacer-36 m-spacer-24"></div>


                        <h3 class="type-24-light">
                            Parking requirements

                        </h3>

                            <div class="spacer-24 m-spacer-16"></div>
                    </div>
                </div>


                    <div class="modern-grid">
                        <div class="column-3 l-column-2 m-column-0"></div>
                        <div class="column-6 l-column-8 m-column-6 newsroom-internal-body">
                            <div class="type-18-light m-type-15">
                                <p>Detached ADUs in Saratoga generally require one uncovered off-street parking space. This requirement is waived if the ADU is located within a half mile of public transit, is part of the existing home or an accessory structure, or is a Junior ADU (JADU).</p>

                            </div>
                            <div class="spacer-24 m-spacer-16"></div>
                        </div>
                    </div>




                    <div class="modern-grid">
                        <div class="column-3 l-column-2 m-column-0"></div>
                        <div class="column-6 l-column-8 m-column-6 newsroom-internal-body">
                            <div class="type-18-light m-type-15">
                                <p>If an existing garage or parking space is removed or converted to create the ADU, it does not need to be replaced.</p>

                            </div>
                            <div class="spacer-24 m-spacer-16"></div>
                        </div>
                    </div>




                <div class="modern-grid">
                    <div class="column-3 l-column-2 m-column-0"></div>
                    <div class="column-6 l-column-8 m-column-6 newsroom-internal-body">
                                <div class="spacer-36 m-spacer-24"></div>


                        <h3 class="type-24-light">
                            Zoning eligibility

                        </h3>

                            <div class="spacer-24 m-spacer-16"></div>
                    </div>
                </div>


                    <div class="modern-grid">
                        <div class="column-3 l-column-2 m-column-0"></div>
                        <div class="column-6 l-column-8 m-column-6 newsroom-internal-body">
                            <div class="type-18-light m-type-15">
                                <p>ADUs are allowed on any property in Saratoga that is zoned for single-family or multi-family use, as long as there is an existing or proposed primary residence on the lot.</p>

                            </div>
                            <div class="spacer-24 m-spacer-16"></div>
                        </div>
                    </div>




